title: Darkmeyer Lantern Shop

properties.value: Darkmeyer Lantern Shop is a store located in Darkmeyer, owned by Grinka Krast. It sells a variety of light sources. Sins of the Father must be completed to access this store. It is one of four stores in Darkmeyer, and is located in the eastern section.

Darkmeyer Lantern Shop is a store located in Darkmeyer, owned by Grinka Krast. It sells a variety of light sources. Sins of the Father must be completed to access this store. It is one of four stores in Darkmeyer, and is located in the eastern section.
